{"tid":6502,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點先可以返去以前咁打RPG","createTime":"2016-11-27T11:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T10:14:57.000Z","uid":17351,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3126446f4461e714e8446c6526606dc907b254c","tid":6502,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"好懷念以前可以一班人打副本，打100次同一個副本都仲打緊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖誕新年大時大節都係同公會網友講聖誕快樂，仲有雙經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知幾時開始PC既RPG好似慢慢沒落，LoL csgo overwatch BF1係好玩，但我都係想玩返RPG升lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n於是我不斷搵返來玩，當然部分冇人玩執左，又有部分game面目全非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。之前搵到隻tree of saviour 諗住玩，點知又好似單機咁打..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟點先可以搵返以前打RPG既感覺，如果有巴打有PC RPG推介都歡迎講出來一齊打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba0757ceb25e22a55dc035ae2f70f0975a49741","tid":6502,"uid":3548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:16:31.000Z","msg":"我都想打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85ec80d45198c9f898d24d05660fba1ef79c71a","tid":6502,"uid":3548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"真係難道沒練習太來感覺都追不回來"},{"pid":"3ccd1baf25c7fafaa67bd3f47c92b586edb58cd6","tid":6502,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係難道沒練習太來感覺都追不回來</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好想識返班人日日打RPG開公會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c351abebc3466d6eafd8db997fe9af71f9c346e","tid":6502,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T23:43:44.000Z","msg":"冇㗎啦，呢代人乜都要快，連打機唔肯花時間，以前嗰種多勞少得嘅game唔再興，冇錢搵就冇人整，你淨係可以懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39388500b24deccd675381ecc478193d4d13f80f","tid":6502,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:46:33.000Z","msg":"一開始諗住隻tos 有啲希望， 屌 ， 單機game 冇交流成份既 交易都要買點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs 未玩已經課左500 玩左一個星期果斷棄"},{"pid":"bacd6a58d9ab72969cdded8c0823a1c88d65042b","tid":6502,"uid":19854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T04:16:51.000Z","msg":"讀書時大時大節同d 網友一齊打活動吹水真係好經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家個心態唔同左，d game 既風格又唔同左，試過玩返但係已經冇左個種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9572e86a85e1965545796dc523c6e33fa73879b5","tid":6502,"uid":616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:12:35.000Z","msg":"Mmorpg比商城類搞死，搞到仲hit既得返一兩隻（e.g. Wow)<br />\n<br />\n所以唔少人寧願玩唔駛/比一次錢既競技類遊戲<br />\n<br />\n同埋玩得mmorpg都要花極大量時間，鍾意玩得既都係會花時間落去既毒撚，競技類嗰d相比之下偽毒mk都唔難花少少時間去玩，所以咪hit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ac8f15c025ecdd07aed65c99c2f1c486d8d59d","tid":6502,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"Ffxiv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傳統mmo類型online game"},{"pid":"a05b338f5d0d60f8e8c57c2ec3af5fbce54145ab","tid":6502,"uid":24587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:35:48.000Z","msg":"諗起之前打ro真係好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6521ba0a5ac6e98c71a6af4455fa13e960d00af","tid":6502,"uid":20951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"FF14"},{"pid":"4f7e44b4290808ac7fa16d722ecc61daf2cbdd7d","tid":6502,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:06:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始諗住隻tos 有啲希望， 屌 ， 單機game 冇交流成份既 交易都要買點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPs 未玩已經課左500 玩左一個星期果斷棄</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對Tos真係好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811424c161d4614e320058c6d3bfed4415971e2c","tid":6502,"uid":27734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T13:38:08.000Z","msg":"我都搵唔返宜種game<br />\n夢之歷險咁多年都仲係我首選online game<br />\n可惜港服已經接近死城<br />\n諗住玩英服但又有時差問題"},{"pid":"db51102478c0381930df98cea67593d91ac83851","tid":6502,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"一路覺得係人大左心境唔同，搞到而定投入唔返。"},{"pid":"3599ca06512e637c73b93c97aab46d6d37586b89","tid":6502,"uid":8373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"記得之前「高X討論區」有個po係搵人玩online game 唔知最尾點"},{"pid":"ab316d685eddc3d41c4e1d48023e14db524958cd","tid":6502,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都搵唔返宜種game<br />\n夢之歷險咁多年都仲係我首選online game<br />\n可惜港服已經接近死城<br />\n諗住玩英服但又有時差問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夢歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣玩到光弓+11"},{"pid":"aa15dd00fda85dfe77f2166b8cb87f759bbd3787","tid":6502,"uid":17351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路覺得係人大左心境唔同，搞到而定投入唔返。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係mmorpg好似都開始沒落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6500f9680588692ff19ddebad103f54704154d83","tid":6502,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T15:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一路覺得係人大左心境唔同，搞到而定投入唔返。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係mmorpg好似都開始沒落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔多唔小因為商城"},{"pid":"6cc42bc5493256b8f41190fef1f0f704b4c5a5bb","tid":6502,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:24:53.000Z","msg":"對上一次玩mmorpg已經係2-3年前，個陣玩開隻game執左，然後就開始少玩電腦<br />\n年幾前電腦壞埋，加上用電腦其實都好麻煩，索性用手機平板代替日常所需<br />\n<br />\n玩左幾年育成類課金手機game，最近認真去諗，哩d根本就唔係我想要嘅野，我想要嘅係以前個種一返到屋企就打開隻game，開始game入面嘅生活<br />\n<br />\n可惜人大左，為自己，為生活，為身邊嘅人，仲邊度有時間同精力花係遊戲入面<br />\n然後就覺得，其實享受唔返以前個種感覺都好正常，亦都覺得以後都唔會再搵得返個種感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提已經戒左課係d垃圾手機game度"},{"pid":"82139dd8fb152b661e81ae5b4e1b6e5537becea2","tid":6502,"uid":3833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ffxiv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傳統mmo類型online game</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻的確係 但係月費實在好貴下"},{"pid":"8cdc49d38346471ab5cda276f173be9998ce7bb8","tid":6502,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"超，你地成日講到幾enjoy mmo <br />\n國際版英文差，唔玩<br />\n要比錢買斷/月費，唔玩<br />\n要練級，唔玩<br />\n要打副本，唔玩<br />\n要打裝，唔玩<br />\n成日都話無以前個種味道，屌，你走去食台灣代理/大陸出個d垃圾game, 你想有幾好味？因為人地target既係當地重課金人士，唔係你地呢d 回憶撚。<br />\n而留番比你地呢d 成日懶感性既自稱老玩家，咪係番炒5/6年前個d 經典之作比你地慢慢懷念囉。<br />\n但又覺得重玩唔抵喎，以前玩落係一招劈死王既高手，要由lv1咩都冇玩番起有邊個會甘心？<br />\n結果就成日覺得無樣岩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每個月都發呢d 廢文係度呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726ce0ea22807b68b47388c5ec4b560677cd41e2","tid":6502,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:44:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ffxiv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n傳統mmo類型online game</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢隻的確係 但係月費實在好貴下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你以前有玩開其他online, 抽商城，買點買裝d 錢夠你玩幾年ffxiv <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d371fcc0636e530e5d894139f53dfcb2c7d17d","tid":6502,"uid":11639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:50:01.000Z","msg":"好懷念以前玩天外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有玩過"},{"pid":"fab94468585a7fdeb3e0c0368c9eb22d0b925ad1","tid":6502,"uid":6424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好懷念以前玩天外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有玩過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，抽武將卡嫁ma<br />\n個陣都幾鐘意玩，<br />\n本來係玩三國，後來又出左水滸傳"},{"pid":"c3f78cf5c982e2261fe087263cde483a71b96980","tid":6502,"uid":47965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T22:43:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}